data.description: Fantastic split level home ready for your cosmetic updates! Spacious living room. Kitchen features white cabinets & appliances and large breakfast/dining area.   Three nice sized bedrooms, two full bathroom are upstairs. Owner's suite features large bathroom with separate shower & tub, double vanity sinks and his & her closets! Finished basement has bedroom with bonus room/living room (or 5th bedroom) and a half bathroom which could be converted to full bath. Enjoy privacy and intimate settings on rear deck. HVAC is new. Don't miss out! A must see!
